videos.headline: Verdell  walks into the end zone for 6-yard TD
videos.description: CJ Verdell breaks a tackle in the backfield and follows his blockers for an easy 6-yard touchdown to put Oregon on the board.

videos.headline: Herbert  connects with Verdell for 18-yard TD
videos.description: On the screen play. Justin Herbert hits CJ Verdell who breaks tackles and runs in a 18-yard touchdown to extend Oregon's lead to 14-3.

videos.headline: Herbert launches ball to Mitchell for 57-yard TD
videos.description: Justin Herbert hits a wide-open Dillon Mitchell for a 57-yard touchdown and a 21-6 Oregon lead.

videos.headline: Crosswell INT recovery leads to a 22-yard TD
videos.description: Frank Darby beats his man on a post route and catches a 22-yard touchdown to cut Oregon's lead to 21-13.

videos.headline: Redd powers in a 8-yard TD
videos.description: Jaylon Redd follow his blockers and punches in a 8-yard touchdown and to give Oregon a 28-13 lead before half.

videos.headline: Wilkins punches in a 1-yard TD, fails on 2-point conversion
videos.description: Manny Wilkins drives in a 1-yard touchdown, but fails to convert the 2-point conversion to tie the game and Arizona State falls to Oregon 31-29.

videos.headline: Wilkins' fumble seals win for Oregon
videos.description: On 3rd-and-9, Manny Wilkins drops back, is hit and fumbles. The ball is recovered by Oregon which seals a 31-29 victory over Arizona State.

videos.headline: ASU defender shoves Oregon center on offside call late in fourth
videos.description: On 3rd-and-2 and 2:12 left on the clock, Arizona State defender jumps and pushes the Oregon center and gets an offside call  lamenting a 31-29 win for Oregon.
